  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Elevated Connectivity Experience",
      "text": "Expand your home connectivity with the AmpliFi HD Mesh Point. This device introduces mesh Wi-Fi technology, transforming your living space into a high-performance wireless network. The system deploys interconnected nodes, each functioning as a mini router to intelligently extend and strengthen the Wi-Fi signal throughout your home, eliminating dead zones for a consistent and robust connection."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Adaptive Connectivity for Every Corner",
      "text": "Operating on the Wi-Fi 5 standard (802.11ac), the AmpliFi mesh system incorporates advanced features like MIMO technology, boasting a 2.4GHz 3x3 configuration and a 5GHz 3x3 setup. This innovative design, with three transmitting and three receiving antennas for both frequency bands, enhances the device's ability to handle multiple data streams simultaneously. The result is improved overall network performance, making it effective in environments with a mix of older and newer devices that operate on different frequency bands."
    }
  ],
